    Install Python 3 stable version

    Install “pip” package by downloading with following url
    https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py

    Update pip and setup tools — `pip install — upgrade pip setuptools`

    pip install virtualenv

    pip install Flask
    
    pip install flask flask-jsonpify flask-sqlalchemy flask-restful flask_cors

    pip install -U scikit-learn

    pip install sklearn pandas matplotlib
    
    

    
    finally open server.py and execute it then the backend will be accessible at port : 5002

    can be checked by entering following url in the browser address bar

    